  "title": "Full-Time Sales Agent",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for a Telesales Agent to acquire commercial customers for electricity plans through outbound calls. You will be responsible for explaining electricity plans clearly, handling objections, and successfully converting leads into completed contracts.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Make outbound calls to potential commercial customers to introduce and promote electricity plans</li><li>Explain electricity plans clearly to customers to help them understand benefits and options</li><li>Handle customer objections effectively to address concerns and move towards closing sales</li><li>Convert leads into completed contracts by guiding customers through the sales process</li><li>Collaborate closely with a supervisor to learn sales techniques and product knowledge through provided training</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate a strong work ethic and willingness to learn new skills through training and supervision</li></ul>",
